e:T511,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you work on old commercial boilers in Nashville?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes — that's one of our specialties. We have five generations of Nashville commercial experience and maintain a parts inventory and supplier network for obsolete components. Most boilers other plumbers tell you are unrepairable, we can actually repair."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you handle commercial water heater warranty work?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We're authorized warranty service for AO Smith, Bradford White, State Industries, and Whirlpool — including their commercial product lines. We file the warranty parts claim and handle the install, you stay focused on running your business."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How fast can you respond to a commercial plumbing emergency in Nashville?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Our emergency service team prioritizes commercial calls during business hours. We aim for same-day arrival on no-hot-water and active-leak situations across Davidson County. For after-hours and weekend commercial emergencies, call the main line and follow the prompts — the on-call plumber will return your call promptly."}}]}6:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.joebsullivanandsons.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://www.joebsullivanandsons.com/services\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Commercial Plumbing & Boiler Service\",\"item\":\"https://www.joebsullivanandsons.com/services/commercial-plumbing\"}]}"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"name\":\"Commercial Plumbing & Boiler Service\",\"description\":\"Nashville's heritage commercial plumber. Boiler diagnostics and repair, commercial water heater service, steam unit repair, backflow, and new construction rough-ins. Licensed master plumber on every job.\",\"serviceType\":\"Commercial Plumbing & Boiler Service\",\"url\":\"https://www.joebsullivanandsons.com/services/commercial-plumbing\",\"provider\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.joebsullivanandsons.com#business\"},\"areaServed\":[{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"East Nashville\"},{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Downtown Nashville\"},{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Green Hills\"},{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Belle Meade & West Nashville\"},{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Brentwood\"},{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Franklin\"}]}"}}],["$","article",null,{"children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"relative h-[260px] sm:h-[340px] lg:h-[420px] overflow-hidden bg-forest-deep","children":[["$","$Lf",null,{"src":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1701421047855-d7bafd8d6f69?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=70","alt":"Commercial boiler room with industrial piping — heritage commercial plumbing in Nashville","fill":true,"priority":true,"sizes":"100vw","className":"object-cover opacity-80"}],["$","div",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-forest-deep/70 via-forest-deep/30 to-transparent"}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-ink/10","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-16","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"lg:col-span-7","children":[["$","nav",null,{"aria-label":"Breadcrumb","className":"text-sm text-ink-muted mb-6","children":["$","ol",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/","className":"hover:text-forest","children":"Home"}]}],["$","li",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"children":"/"}],["$","li",null,{"children":["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/services","className":"hover:text-forest","children":"Services"}]}],["$","li",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"children":"/"}],["$","li",null,{"className":"text-ink","children":"Commercial Service"}]]}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"eyebrow mb-4","children":"Service"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.05] text-ink mb-6","children":["Commercial Plumbing & Boiler Service"," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"italic text-forest","children":"in Nashville"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"font-display italic text-2xl text-ink-soft mb-7","children":"Heritage commercial plumbing. Same family since 1895."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed","children":"Joe B. Sullivan & Sons has been doing commercial plumbing in Nashville for five generations — we've serviced churches, schools, restaurants, retail buildings, multi-family properties, hotels, and industrial facilities across Davidson County. Our specialty within commercial work is boiler diagnostics, repair, and commercial water heater installation. When a 30-year-old building has a boiler nobody else wants to touch because the parts are obsolete, we usually have the part on the truck or know exactly where to source it."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"lg:col-span-5","children":["$","$L10",null,{"defaultService":"commercial-plumbing"}]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 lg:py-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-editorial","children":[["$","div","Boiler diagnostics and repair",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Boiler diagnostics and repair"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We work on commercial boilers across Nashville — gas-fired hot water boilers, low-pressure steam, atmospheric and power-burner units, and the older cast-iron sectional boilers that still heat plenty of Nashville's pre-war buildings. Our master plumber Frank Sullivan has been on commercial boiler service in this market for decades; if the unit is repairable, we'll keep it running. When replacement is the right answer, we install AERCO, Lochinvar, Weil-McLain, and Burnham units depending on the load and the building's footprint. We also pull permits and coordinate state boiler inspection where required."}]]}],["$","div","Commercial water heaters",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Commercial water heaters"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Restaurants, hotels, multi-family properties, and industrial laundries in Nashville all run different commercial water heater configurations — large-volume gas units, electric, indirect-fired off a boiler, or hybrid setups. We install, service, and warranty AO Smith, State Industries, Bradford White, and Rheem commercial units, and we know how to size correctly for actual peak demand (a Nashville hotel breakfast hour or a restaurant's 6:00 PM dish load is very different from residential peak demand). Replacement turnarounds are typically 24–72 hours for in-stock units."}]]}],["$","div","Steam unit and old-building expertise",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Steam unit and old-building expertise"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Half of Nashville's commercial inventory is pre-1980, and a lot of it still runs on systems most plumbers don't service: low-pressure steam, gravity hot water, galvanized supply lines, and discontinued fixtures and parts. Joe B. Sullivan & Sons has maintained an extensive knowledge base of obsolete and discontinued parts — five generations of accumulated expertise on what's actually in Nashville's older buildings. If a national chain plumber tells you a steam radiator valve isn't repairable and the whole system needs replacement, get a second opinion. Most of the time it's repairable."}]]}],["$","div","New construction and tenant build-outs",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"New construction and tenant build-outs"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We do full commercial plumbing rough-ins and trim-outs across the Nashville metro — restaurants, retail, light industrial, and multi-family. We coordinate with GCs, MEP engineers, and permit offices, and we work to specification (or call out a spec issue early if we see one). We also do tenant fit-outs on a fast-track schedule when leases are signed and the clock is running. Bonded and insured for commercial work, master-plumber-supervised on every job."}]]}]]}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-bone-100/60 border-y border-ink/10 py-16 lg:py-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"eyebrow mb-3","children":"Common questions"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-ink mb-10 leading-tight","children":["Frequently asked about ","commercial service"," in Nashville."]}],["$","dl",null,{"className":"space-y-6","children":[["$","div","Do you work on old commercial boilers in Nashville?",{"className":"card-press p-6","children":[["$","dt",null,{"className":"font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3","children":"Do you work on old commercial boilers in Nashville?"}],["$","dd",null,{"className":"text-ink-muted leading-relaxed","children":"Yes — that's one of our specialties. We have five generations of Nashville commercial experience and maintain a parts inventory and supplier network for obsolete components. Most boilers other plumbers tell you are unrepairable, we can actually repair."}]]}],["$","div","Can you handle commercial water heater warranty work?",{"className":"card-press p-6","children":[["$","dt",null,{"className":"font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3","children":"Can you handle commercial water heater warranty work?"}],["$","dd",null,{"className":"text-ink-muted leading-relaxed","children":"Yes. We're authorized warranty service for AO Smith, Bradford White, State Industries, and Whirlpool — including their commercial product lines. We file the warranty parts claim and handle the install, you stay focused on running your business."}]]}],["$","div","How fast can you respond to a commercial plumbing emergency in Nashville?",{"className":"card-press p-6","children":[["$","dt",null,{"className":"font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3","children":"How fast can you respond to a commercial plumbing emergency in Nashville?"}],["$","dd",null,{"className":"text-ink-muted leading-relaxed","children":"Our emergency service team prioritizes commercial calls during business hours. We aim for same-day arrival on no-hot-water and active-leak situations across Davidson County. For after-hours and weekend commercial emergencies, call the main line and follow the prompts — the on-call plumber will return your call promptly."}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 lg:py-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mb-10","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"eyebrow mb-3","children":"Service areas"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-ink leading-tight","children":["We provide ","commercial service"," across these Nashville-area neighborhoods:"]}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3","children":[["$","li","east-nashville",{"children":["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/areas/east-nashville","className":"block py-3 px-4 border border-ink/10 hover:border-forest hover:bg-bone-100/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-ink","children":"East Nashville"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"block text-xs text-ink-muted mt-0.5","children":"Nashville, TN"}]]}]}],["$","li","downtown-nashville",{"children":["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/areas/downtown-nashville","className":"block py-3 px-4 border border-ink/10 hover:border-forest hover:bg-bone-100/50 transition